ualitativ ausgerichteten Distributionsanalysen struktureller und orthographischer Varianten von Präposition-Definitartikel-Verbindungen basieren.  aThis book describes and compares at different systemic levels the contractions of prepositions and articles in German and Italian, two languages that are representative of divergent grammatical development. The author's intra and inter lingual analyses consider both diachronic and synchronic aspects and are empirically supported by large-scale quantitative and qualitative corpus investigations.  afunded by Institut für Deutsche Sprache  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access. Unless otherwise specified individually in the content, the work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives (CC BY-NC-ND) license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 0aGerman languagexArticles. 0aGerman languagexGrammar, ComparativexItalian. 0aGerman languagexPrepositions. 0aItalian languagexArticles. 0aItalian languagexGrammar, ComparativexGerman. 0aItalian languagexPrepositions. 4aBestimmter Artikel. 4aKlitisierung. 4aPräposition. 4aVerschmelzung. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aCliticization.  aContraction.  aDefinite Article.  aPreposition.2 aInstitut für Deutsche Spracheefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z97831107195500 cEPUBz97831105580810 cprintz978311055790940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110557862zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110557862zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110557862.jpg  a978-3-11-071955-0 DG Plus eBo